```

**Helper commands** available at any time:
- `/flow-status` - Check current position
- `/flow-next` - Auto-advance to next step
- `/flow-rollback` - Undo last change
- `/flow-phase`, `/flow-task`, `/flow-iteration` - Add structure as needed

